Use the standard library
This is how to pairs_sum_to_zero of l:
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this l's length times:
      Remember that j is sum of i and 1
      Do this (diff of l's length and j) times:
         When (sum of (item i in l) and (item j in l)) is 0, then:
            Increase count
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is count
Now you know

>>> pairs_sum_to_zero of [1, 3, 5, 0]
0
>>> pairs_sum_to_zero of [1, 3, -2, 1]
0
>>> pairs_sum_to_zero of [1, 2, 3, 7]
0